# JS Modules Reference

41 JS files under `assets/system/js/`, loaded via `assets/system/config.js` → `passages/0 - System/storyJavaScript.js`.

## Load Order (defined in `config.js`)

```
utils  →  ui  →  modal  →  system
```

Each group loaded sequentially; within a group, array order matters.

## File Catalog

### `utils/` — Base helpers (load first)

| File | Global API | Purpose |
|------|-----------|---------|
| `jobSchedule.js` | `window.jobSchedule` | Off-days / work-days lookup for topbar + calendar |
| `modal.js` | `window.Modal`, `window.ModalTabSystem` | Create/manage modal overlays with tabs |
| `tooltip.js` | `$.fn.initTooltips` | Attach tooltips to info icons |
| `notification.js` | `window.notify` | Toast notifications |
| `accordion.js` | `window.initAccordion` | Collapsible section binder |

