## Event Hooks Attached (cross-module)

| Event | Handlers |
|-------|----------|
| `:passagestart` | `location.js` (clear bg), `layout.js` |
| `:passagerender` | `layout.js` (wrap), `location.js` (inject bg), `topbar.js`, `rightbar.js` |
| `:passageend` | `saveload.js` (auto-save to slot 0) |
| `:storyready` | Module init hooks |

